item.title: whale. big. boat. little.
item.description: I love flickr. it is great. My friend thom has posted what could be one of the most amazing pictures i have ever seen. check it out here. Last night i saw mike and his friends at clark’s. it ruled. however i had a horrible headache. HORRIBLE. so i went home. went to bed. slept. woke up. still had a headache. called in sick. slept. until 3:00. woke up. still had a headache.
